one physical Machine running multiple Logical Machine is Hardware based Virtual Machine

Advantage:
   1.Hardware Resources sharing 
   
   
   
These Virtual Machines access to run a particular programming languages applications
     1.JVM-Java Virtual Machine (Access Run Time Engine to run Java based Application)
     2.PVM-Paret Virtual Machine (Access Run Time Engine to run Perl based Application)
     3.CLR-Common Language Runtime (Access Run Time Engine to run Dot Net based Application)
     
     
JVM -  is part of JRE
    2. to load and run the .class file     
